  <brief_title>Hematoma Block as an Adjunct to Procedural Sedation for Forearm Fracture Reduction</brief_title>
  <official_title>Hematoma Blocks in Forearm Fractures: An Effective Adjunct to Procedural Sedation?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
